baseName.value: Extreme section – PVC window 1,23m x 1,48m: PVC Aluminium sheet - Double Glazing

generalComment.value:
"Geographical coverage: products manufactured and installed in France and Italy
Temporal coverage: production and installation in 2022
Technological coverage: see. “Description of product” in section 2"


Manufacturing consumptions were allocated physically (by mass and window unit).


Cut-off criteria were implemented in compliance with standards NF EN 15804+A2 and NF EN 15804+A2/CN (1% per elementary process, 5% per stage, in mass and use of primary energy).

technologicalApplicability.value:
The covered products are the 1,23m*1,48m PVC windows made of Extreme PVC sections with double or triple Glazing (8 or 12mm glass thickness) and double leaf
 "Thermal insulation Uw = 1,3 W/ m2.K for double glazing
Thermal insulation Uw = 1,0 W/ m2.K for triple glazing"
